    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 1994 Nissan Skyline GT-R V-Spec II. The RB26DETT power plant retains its factory-honed precision, delivering linear boost across the rev range with zero shaft play in the twin ceramic turbochargers. The ATTESA E-TS pro-active torque-split system operates flawlessly, paired with a crisp 5-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip rear differential. This example features the original V-Spec II Brembo calipers and BBS forged wheels. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, showing original factory welds and bushings in exceptional condition. Recent compression tests across all six cylinders show negligible variance, confirming the mechanical integrity of this legendary platform.",
      "price": 48500.0,
